  m_text: "Controls: WASD + Spacebar\n\nQuiz minigame: Go to the school (cube)\nControls:
    Point and click\n\nSalmon minigame: Go to the river\nControls: Spacebar to charge
    claw.\nCatch 10 fish to \"win\".\n\nBerry minigame: Go to the berry bush.\nControls
